oai_dc:dc.dc:title: A Case of Papillomatous Digital Dermatitis in Feedyard Cattle
oai_dc:dc.dc:creator: Lubbers, Brian V.
Apley, Michael
oai_dc:dc.dc:subject: Papillomatous digital dermatitis
feedlot cattle
diagnostic plan
treatment options
atypical presentation
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: Papillomatous digital dermatitis may be an emerging disease within the feeder cattle industry. This case report will review the presentation, diagnostic plan and some of the available treatment options as well as describe an atypical presentation of this disease.
